urs at 00:00, 08:00, and 16:00 UTC, using a time-weighted average premium between the perpetual contract and spot price. The platform applies a ±0.375% funding rate cap with a 0.01% baseline rate. Due to MEXC's zero maker fees, traders can execute funding arbitrage strategies without additional trading costs when providing liquidity."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
